|A| = \max\{|a_{ij}| : i = 1,\ldots,n \text{ and} j = 1,\ldots,m\}
 |AB| \leq m|A||B|
 |AB| = \max\{| \sum_{j=1}^{m}a_{ij}b_{jk} |: i = 1,\ldots,n \text{ and } k = 1,\ldots,p\} \leq \max\{ \sum_{j=1}^{m}|a_{ij}b_{jk}| : i = 1,\ldots,n \text{ and } k = 1,\ldots,p\}  \leq m\max\{|a_ij|\}\max\{|b_{jk}|\} = m|A||B| 
